Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.34,0:01:39.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在很久以前有一群生物
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.85,0:01:42.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,低等而且離奇
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.58,0:01:46.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是與常見動植物截然不同的一群生物
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.35,0:01:49.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這群微妙的成員
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.94,0:01:52.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從遠古以來人們就非常敬畏
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.82,0:01:54.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道何時開始
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.25,0:01:56.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稱它們為「蟲」
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.75,0:02:31.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早安  翠
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.81,0:02:35.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早安  比齊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.27,0:02:47.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天感覺怎樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.01,0:02:50.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,眼睛還痛嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.08,0:02:52.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了  比齊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.90,0:02:53.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.23,0:02:55.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告訴比齊你一件事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.45,0:02:58.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.03,0:03:01.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個病的原因
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.27,0:03:05.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是因為蟲子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.89,0:03:11.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直寄居在我的眼睛裡面
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.80,0:03:17.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,翠是遠房親戚家的女兒
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.49,0:03:19.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,半年前
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.14,0:03:23.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得了一看見光眼睛就疼痛難忍的病
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.46,0:03:32.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是種任何一個眼醫都找不出原因的怪病
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.27,0:03:35.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在還沒有找到治療方法的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.52,0:03:38.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使只看見一絲的光線也會十分疼痛了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.17,0:03:47.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為此  在我家一個不見天日的嚴實的倉庫裡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.61,0:03:49.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,翠一個人被留下來了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.14,0:03:54.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那樣做或許是為了翠著想
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.87,0:03:55.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但在我看來
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.14,0:03:58.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,翠是被拋棄在這裡的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.71,0:04:17.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在眼瞼裡面還有另一個眼瞼在
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.17,0:04:19.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.08,0:04:26.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那裡是外面的光絕對照不進去的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.48,0:04:29.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蟲就在那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.90,0:04:31.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第二層眼瞼？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.85,0:04:32.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.99,0:04:35.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比齊不知道閉上它的方法嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.11,0:04:37.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我來教你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.16,0:04:39.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把眼睛閉上
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.72,0:04:40.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.15,0:04:43.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看見什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.31,0:04:46.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒…什麼也…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.64,0:04:47.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.63,0:04:53.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像有什麼東西閃爍著
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.75,0:04:55.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在眼睛裡游動
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.55,0:04:58.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.00,0:05:00.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使閉上了一層眼瞼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.44,0:05:03.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,眼睛還在看著眼瞼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.04,0:05:05.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,並沒有真正閉上
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.42,0:05:09.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.00,0:05:12.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果想要看到真正的黑暗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.51,0:05:17.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就得閉上那層能看見閃爍物的眼瞼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.99,0:05:21.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那樣的話
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.41,0:05:25.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真正的黑暗才會降臨
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.84,0:05:42.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我做不到啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.40,0:05:43.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.82,0:05:45.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比齊好笨
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.35,0:06:01.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們在漆黑中玩耍
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.85,0:06:06.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然在進入倉庫的一瞬間
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.74,0:06:08.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,確實什麼都看不見
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.51,0:06:10.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是等過了一會
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.15,0:06:14.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就能在黑暗中大概看到物體的輪廓
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.48,0:06:22.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼看得見呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.74,0:06:25.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明是一片漆黑的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.20,0:06:29.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地下有條光河在流淌喲
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.68,0:06:35.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把兩層眼瞼閉上就能看到了喲
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.79,0:06:38.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直處於完全的黑暗中
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.23,0:06:44.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就能看到許多從遠方過來的光斑
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.54,0:06:47.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逐漸交匯成洪水一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.18,0:06:51.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些光
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.89,0:06:54.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是仔細看的話就發現全部是細小的蟲子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.19,0:06:59.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是當我想要更加接近去看的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.92,0:07:02.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.00,0:07:12.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要再接近那條河了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.59,0:07:16.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是一個我見都沒有見過的人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.80,0:07:22.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那獨眼的男人總在河的彼岸制止我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.02,0:07:24.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.04,0:07:27.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我總是在這邊望著
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.16,0:07:29.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.86,0:07:34.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不時會感到不安
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.51,0:07:56.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,閉上了雙眼的翠看到的那些東西
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.96,0:07:57.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.72,0:08:04.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是什麼呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.10,0:08:12.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比齊  你總是在倉庫裡待太久了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.84,0:08:16.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經把替換的眼帶都燒乾淨了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.18,0:08:19.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,食具也消毒了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.00,0:08:25.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.73,0:08:28.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不能保證不被傳染啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.09,0:08:32.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本家的那些人們
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.77,0:08:35.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是因為害怕這樣才把翠拋棄了的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.50,0:08:37.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我們要…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.99,0:08:39.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.84,0:08:41.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,確實如此
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.27,0:08:45.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個孩子是好孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.69,0:08:48.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽必須寬厚一些
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.71,0:08:58.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了不讓那孩子心中的光消失
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.82,0:09:01.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會讓她跟著我們的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.41,0:09:05.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是求你了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.68,0:09:10.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要也染上那種病
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.14,0:09:15.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.27,0:09:23.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會來…這裡嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.18,0:10:17.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了  剛才是？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.92,0:10:20.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.35,0:10:25.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.67,0:10:28.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.60,0:10:30.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.93,0:10:59.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比齊  還在睡嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.24,0:11:03.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比齊！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.78,0:11:16.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比齊？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.77,0:11:21.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比齊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.82,0:11:26.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.58,0:11:33.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比齊  不會再來了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.01,0:11:38.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的病已經傳染給他了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.06,0:11:50.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是你的錯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.32,0:11:55.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這會傳染的病的錯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.80,0:12:15.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.76,0:12:17.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把窗子打開的話比齊會…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.77,0:12:19.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.83,0:12:24.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是這方面的專家
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.63,0:12:29.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,治療藥和鎮痛劑已經給他喝了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.13,0:12:32.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是把他關在黑暗中
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.87,0:12:34.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反而會使病情更加惡化
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.51,0:12:37.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是什麼人？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.94,0:12:39.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  真是失敬
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.22,0:12:43.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鄙人是蟲師銀古
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.82,0:12:47.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我聽說了倉庫裡的女孩的傳聞
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.54,0:12:53.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那不是眼醫能治的病
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.64,0:12:56.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有我們蟲師才能治療
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.27,0:13:00.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比齊呢？這個孩子能治好嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.68,0:13:05.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  他體內的蟲子好象才剛孵化不久
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.51,0:13:09.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要用藥治療應該就有效果了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.54,0:13:19.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比齊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.79,0:13:23.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比齊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.44,0:13:28.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比齊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.90,0:13:34.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.12,0:13:38.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.91,0:13:40.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.56,0:13:42.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,翠
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.87,0:13:51.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你醒來了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.72,0:13:57.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,眼睛還痛嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.28,0:13:59.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…不痛了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.48,0:14:03.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好  有效果了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.09,0:14:06.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,翠的病因
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.82,0:14:08.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是一種叫「黑暗瞳蟲」的蟲引起的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.73,0:14:11.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通過黑暗繁殖
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.59,0:14:17.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你和翠在黑暗中相處時間太久了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.93,0:14:20.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你認識翠嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.83,0:14:23.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,獨眼…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.99,0:14:26.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我閉上第二層眼瞼的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.47,0:14:28.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到那孩子在對岸
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.77,0:14:35.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那條光流和地上的河不同
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.94,0:14:38.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太接近的話  眼睛會中毒
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.49,0:14:41.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他有左眼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.22,0:14:45.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是翠所說的那個獨眼男人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.33,0:14:50.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日落後就開始翠的治療
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.20,0:14:53.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.10,0:14:55.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.10,0:15:19.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,翠
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.07,0:15:22.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.72,0:15:25.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明都說了不要接近那條河的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.50,0:15:41.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,翠
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.14,0:15:59.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,翠的眼球已經壞死了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.99,0:16:02.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.93,0:16:03.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總會有辦法的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.36,0:16:08.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩層眼瞼合上太久的話
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.53,0:16:10.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,眼睛就會被黑暗所吞噬
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.24,0:16:14.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  聽好  翠
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.16,0:16:16.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,利用月光把蟲子引出來
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.15,0:16:20.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就在閉著第二層眼瞼的同時
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.77,0:16:23.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慢慢睜開眼睛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.85,0:16:46.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快出來  蟲子們
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.22,0:16:48.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是光哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.00,0:17:12.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蟲…蟲子？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.05,0:17:25.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.76,0:17:28.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,翠  可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.24,0:17:29.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把眼睛閉上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.09,0:17:57.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.30,0:18:02.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來  該治翠的眼球了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.24,0:18:04.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蟲…蟲子…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.25,0:18:08.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的在眼睛裡…有蟲子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.11,0:18:11.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然已經廢了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.85,0:18:14.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道能不能行
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.46,0:18:23.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把這個給翠安上
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.29,0:18:27.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你從剛才開始就驚訝個不停
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.33,0:18:30.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別緊張
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.77,0:18:31.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是義眼而已
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.93,0:18:34.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是剛才那種液態的蟲
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.81,0:18:36.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把這個注入的話
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.83,0:18:38.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算只是普通的玻璃球
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.20,0:18:40.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也能起到眼球的功用
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.66,0:18:49.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個  我能問個問題嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.91,0:18:54.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們所看到的光流的真面目
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.21,0:18:56.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.89,0:19:00.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,閉上兩層眼瞼自己看看
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.64,0:19:05.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你忘記了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.04,0:19:09.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑暗的通道就會打開
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.57,0:19:15.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你以前不也是那樣嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.42,0:19:29.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,據說人類從擁有了光明起 
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.43,0:19:32.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就忘記了閉上第二層眼瞼的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.73,0:19:39.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過對於生物來說或許是件好事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.85,0:19:45.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前就有很多人類因為注視「它」太久
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.18,0:19:49.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失去了眼球
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.32,0:19:57.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第二層眼瞼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.92,0:20:00.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真正的黑暗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.29,0:20:02.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,異樣的光
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.53,0:20:15.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是活躍於我們腳下的無數生命
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.39,0:20:18.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,匯集而成的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.31,0:20:25.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「嘭」地眼前一亮
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.22,0:20:28.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這之後一瞬間是完全的黑暗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.04,0:20:30.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,越過腳下
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.67,0:20:36.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到一條一直向下流淌著的光流
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.24,0:20:43.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然只是那位蟲師給翠安上眼球的一刹那
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.95,0:20:47.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太漂亮了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.94,0:20:49.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仿佛能把人的身體吸進去
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.18,0:20:52.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真想一直看下去
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.58,0:20:59.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穿好了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.46,0:21:05.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,翠走出了倉庫
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.02,0:21:10.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到了樹  花  陽光等很多東西
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.96,0:21:12.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.70,0:21:18.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會在黑暗中沉迷於那些不可思議的光了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.98,0:21:25.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個人也是因為做了和翠一樣的事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.65,0:21:29.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而失去了真正的左眼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.10,0:23:37.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(800,0)}「柔軟的角」


